{"tid":761650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「千年一見美少女」曬素顏美照　網民：沒身材也無所謂了","createTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T12:41:39.000Z","uid":9573,"like":19,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"01727d7822045a039155618771bdb4e8e58814f9","tid":761650,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5b5ed41649e7bf4adb96938b_201807301702.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5b5ed41649e7bf4adb96938b_201807301702.png&h=7fdc0da8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本女星橋本環奈五官精緻。<br />\n<br />\n有「千年一見美少女」美譽的19歲日本女星橋本環奈，靠著一張如漫畫走出現實的絕美五官爆紅，近日在真人電影《銀魂》飾演「神樂」一角更讓她人氣破表，日前她在推特PO出多張素顏照，引發網友瘋狂點讚轉推，更有人直言：「如果有這張臉蛋，身材不好也無所謂了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5b5ed474985d5e4adcf630d3_201807301703.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b5ed474985d5e4adcf630d3_201807301703.png&h=7b84ed60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈PO出素顏照。<br />\n<br />\n走紅後的橋本環奈經常在社群與粉絲互動，近日她一連上傳數張素顏照，照片中她穿著休閒戴上膠框眼鏡，雖然頭髮有些凌亂，但一張純淨無暇的白皙美顏，以及一雙靈性十足的﻿維港灣兩房月租2.4萬無辜大眼，讓網友完全無法抵擋女神魅力，紛紛留言表示：「果然是仙女」、「美哭」，還有人笑說身高152公分的她雖是五短身材，但只要有這張臉，「身材不好也無所謂了！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5b5ed49949e7bf4adb96938d_201807301704.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b5ed49949e7bf4adb96938d_201807301704.png&h=fe9254bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈素顏曝光。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cxjmt9f1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcxjmt9f1&h=3f5a3687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲網友瘋狂轉推橋本環奈素顏照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.nownews.com/nownews_production/images/5b5ed56a5a2b384b19271f20_201807301707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.nownews.com%2Fnownews_production%2Fimages%2F5b5ed56a5a2b384b19271f20_201807301707.jpg&h=5745bcd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲橋本環奈個頭嬌小，身高僅152公分。"},{"pid":"bf57d651f5c1a93aa33ec560eb274b604fd92fc8","tid":761650,"uid":34495,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"雖然頭髮有些凌亂，但一張純淨無暇的白皙美顏，以及一雙靈性十足的﻿維港灣兩房月租2.4萬無辜大眼，讓網友完全無法抵擋女神魅力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfafc71a6fcb82a023cb391f72f53d6583e60c9c","tid":761650,"uid":99364,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef4bea800ab91fb98d02502b756fa081d0485f2e","tid":761650,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce840cd5df310d0afe055020b53f6e380854805c","tid":761650,"uid":135445,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個覺得好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本吹大左"},{"pid":"0e623dda203acb5b013bf631b971537285a4a3b1","tid":761650,"uid":63163,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"以及一雙靈性十足的﻿<span style=\"color: red;\">維港灣兩房月租2.4萬</span>無辜大眼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dade805b00f36e9d821ecfef4605c38acee0f6","tid":761650,"uid":114090,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"千雪BB世界第一！"},{"pid":"6317afdceabb482ae050b67508351f3300a7dd44","tid":761650,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bfafc71a6fcb82a023cb391f72f53d6583e60c9c","tid":761650,"uid":99364,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,